  "keyFeatures": [
    "Zero-shot voice cloning from a short reference audio clip",
    "Voice design via text attributes (gender, age, pitch, accent, dialect)",
    "Support for 600+ languages with language-agnostic and language-specified modes",
    "Diffusion language model architecture with RTF as low as 0.025",
    "Non-verbal sound synthesis (laughter, sighs, etc.) and pronunciation control",
    "Batch inference across multiple GPUs for large-scale TTS tasks",
    "Long-form generation with automatic text chunking and cross-fade",
    "Fine-tuning support from pretrained checkpoints on custom data"
  ],
